Street rapper, Olamide has finally stepped out with the musical video of his controversial track "Science Student". In this visual, the rapper walks through a building filled with drug addicts abusing drugs in different ways unimaginable. The father of one later comes out of the building dancing with a group of people dressed in an African style and at the end the song comes to a finish with "Say No To Drugs". Kaffy is behind the creative direction of the clips while the video was shot and directed by Unlimited L.A. Check it out.